---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Grandevity" lang="en">
  <main class="legal-container">
    <header class="legal-header">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Effective Date: 2026-05-05</p>
    </header>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <p>Welcome to <strong>Grandevity Limited</strong> ("Website", "Service", "we", "our", or "us"), accessible from grandevity.co.nz. This Privacy Policy explains how information may be collected, used, and protected when visitors access our website, HTML5 browser games (e.g., Kiwi Defenders), and related digital services.</p>
      
      <p>This policy is designed to comply with global online privacy standards and the strict requirements of advertising networks, including Google AdSense.</p>

      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect limited types of information automatically when users visit the Website or play our games. This may include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Browser type, version, and operating system</li>
        <li>Screen resolution and language preferences</li>
        <li>Referring website or source</li>
        <li>Gameplay statistics, save data, and session duration</li>
        <li>Internet Protocol (IP) address (anonymized where applicable)</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Game Save Data:</strong> For our interactive HTML5 games, progress, high scores, and user preferences are saved locally on your device using standard browser storage (Local Storage/IndexedDB). This data remains on your device and is not transmitted to our backend servers.</p>
      <p>We do not intentionally collect personally identifiable information unless voluntarily submitted by the user through contact forms or email communication.</p>

      <h2>2. Cookies and Similar Technologies</h2>
      <p>Our Website uses cookies and similar technologies to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Improve website performance and loading speeds</li>
        <li>Save gameplay preferences and tactical upgrades</li>
        <li>Analyze traffic and visitor behavior</li>
        <li>Support third-party advertising services</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Users may disable cookies through their browser settings. However, some features of the Website or game save systems may not function properly after disabling cookies.</p>

      <h2>3. Google AdSense and Advertising</h2>
      <p>We use third-party advertising services including Google AdSense to display advertisements on the Website.</p>
      <p>Google and its partners use cookies, including the <strong>DoubleClick DART cookie</strong>, to serve personalized ads based on your visits to this Website and other websites across the internet. Google may collect and process data according to its own privacy policies.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Users can learn more about how Google uses data here: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Advertising Policies</a></li>
        <li>Users can manage personalized advertising settings here: <a href="https://myadcenter.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ad Settings</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>Our Website and games may integrate third-party services such as analytics providers (e.g., Google Analytics), advertising networks, and game distribution platforms (e.g., CrazyGames, GameDistribution). These third parties may independently collect data according to their own privacy policies. We do not control the privacy practices of external websites or services.</p>

      <h2>5. Children’s Privacy</h2>
      <p>Our games are intended for general audiences. Grandevity Limited does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13 (or the applicable age of consent in your region). If a parent or guardian believes a child has provided personal information, please contact us to request prompt removal.</p>

      <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to help protect the Website and associated data from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure. However, no internet transmission or electronic storage method can be guaranteed to be completely secure.</p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your country or region, you may have rights regarding your personal data, including requesting access to, correction of, or deletion of stored data, or objecting to certain data processing activities. Requests may be submitted through our official contact channels.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect legal requirements, technology updates, or advertising policy changes. Updated versions will be published on this page with a revised effective date.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact Information</h2>
      <p>If you have questions regarding this Privacy Policy, you may contact us through the Website contact page or via official business inquiries.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-container { 
    padding: 4rem 5%; 
    max-width: 800px; 
    margin: 0 auto; 
    min-height: 70vh; 
    color: #cbd5e1;
  }
  .legal-header { 
    text-align: center; 
    margin-bottom: 3rem; 
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .legal-header h1 { 
    font-size: 2.5rem; 
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem; 
    color: #f8fafc; 
  }
  .legal-header p { 
    color: #64748b; 
    font-size: 1rem; 
  }
  .legal-content h2 { 
    color: #f8fafc; 
    font-size: 1.5rem; 
    margin-top: 2.5rem; 
    margin-bottom: 1rem; 
  }
  .legal-content p { 
    line-height: 1.7; 
    margin-bottom: 1rem; 
  }
  .legal-content ul { 
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem; 
    padding-left: 1.5rem; 
  }
  .legal-content li { 
    line-height: 1.6; 
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem; 
  }
  .legal-content a {
    color: #38bdf8;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .legal-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>